Notes:
------

avconv version used:
git e998b56 (2013-08-29)

avconf configure options used:
./configure --enable-libx264 --enable-libpulse --enable-gpl --enable-libmp3lame

Nice usage examples for avconv and other tools:
http://www.cit-ec.de/sites/www.cit-ec.de/files/videosync.pdf

Hint: The libav doc/ directory also contains an easy to read html version of
the avconf manual page (run "make documentation").

Usefull tools:
--------------

MP4Box:
concatenating mp4 files and other basic manipulations
apt-get install gpac

mp4joiner:
concatenating mp4 files (had troubles with MP4Box an avconv):
http://www.mp4joiner.org/en/

mp4info:
querying basing infos (e.g. resulition, fps) from mp4 files
apt-get install mp4v2-utils

